startting admin mode
====================
stop the servers
./enchryptproperties.sh
./configdb.sh
./updatedb.sh
/opt/IBM/SMP/maximo/tools/maximo

check the configuration
maximo.properties  (file location)
opt/IBM/SMP/maximo/applications/maximo/properties/maximo.properties.orig/maximo.properties
/opt/IBM/SMP/maximo/applications/maximo/properties/maximo.properties

now start admin mode
/opt/IBM/SMP/maximo/tools/maximo/internal
./setAdminMode -mON
./setAdminMode -mOFF

